Package: jbdtool
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: CLI tool for JBD Battery Management Systems
 jbdtool communicates with JBD BMS devices over serial, CAN, Bluetooth,
 and TCP/IP transports. Supports reading/writing battery parameters and
 JSON output.
